name: The Adventure Begins
description:
Artist and BEANSDAO co-founder, @bodegacatceo, invites viewers into the world of Beans by featuring the first 5 randomly generated beans (Bean #0-4) as a way to celebrate the successful launch of BEANSDAO mainnet.

BEANSDAO is an on-chain, open-source, cc0 fork of Nouns on ethereum mainnet.

The project mission is to support creatives in web3 and innovate with our characters, the beans (or beanlings), in a decentralized environment

Find out more or bid on our daily NFT auctions
www.beans.wtf
